author: @OmkarSapre
text:
The agency that shot this needs severe attention to detail! There are continuity errors in the film.

The girls in the video are seen in different spots within the bus at different times.

At 0.1 the boy sees two girls on the right side of the bus, positioned behind him. At 0.3, the same two girls are on the right side of the bus and positioned in front of him.

At 0.22, a red hair girl is at the right side. (She has moved there at 0.7.). A girl with brown dots on an off-white shirt is on the left side.

At 0.25, the boy turns around, the red hair girl and brown dots girl have changed positions. A new girl in a maroon shirt, not seen earlier, has now appeared. 

Just at the next second (0.26), the boy returns to his position, the red hair girl and brown dots girl are back to their earlier positions, and the maroon-shirt girl is in a new position.

Also, the collar position of the central girl character (Janhvi) is different at 0.10, changes at 0.11, and moves back at 0.12, and so does the position of her thumb wrt the first C of Coca-Cola.
